<h1 class="page-title">Our Ethos</h1>

<p class="intro">
  We are a student-driven community passionate about AI and ML, committed to hands-on learning, collaboration, 
  and ethical innovation. Our club thrives on curiosity, experimentation, and sharing knowledge — empowering 
  students to transform ideas into real-world solutions while fostering an inclusive, responsible, and vibrant 
  AI ecosystem.
</p>

<h2 class="section-heading">Our Principles</h2>

<ul class="ethos-list">
  <li><strong>Curiosity First:</strong> We question, explore, break things, and learn by doing.</li>
  <li><strong>Collaboration Always:</strong> We grow together, lifting each other up.</li>
  <li><strong>Ethical Innovation:</strong> We develop AI responsibly, keeping people at the center.</li>
  <li><strong>Openness:</strong> We share knowledge freely — no gatekeeping.</li>
  <li><strong>Impact Focus:</strong> Projects aim to create meaningful real-world solutions.</li>
  <li><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> Every skill level, background, and perspective is welcome.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="section-heading">Writing Culture</h2>

<ul class="ethos-list">
  <li><strong>Clear & Simple:</strong> Explain like you're talking to a friend.</li>
  <li><strong>Honest:</strong> No pretending — share what you know and what you learned.</li>
  <li><strong>Helpful:</strong> Your writing should teach, not intimidate.</li>
  <li><strong>Evidence-backed:</strong> Claims come with examples, data, or logic.</li>
  <li><strong>Community-focused:</strong> Write to help Neural Hive grow stronger together.</li>
</ul>

